A vibrant Studio Ghibli style illustration of Singapore's Marina Bay skyline at golden hour, with hundreds of colorful paper lanterns rising into a warm amber sky, each lantern unique in color and pattern. In the foreground, a diverse crowd of tiny animated figures stand on a grassy hill, arms raised releasing their lanterns upward. The scene conveys a sense of collective awakening and celebration, with lush tropical trees framing the edges. The iconic Singapore Flyer and distinctive architecture are rendered in soft, dreamy watercolor-like strokes with gentle gradients of orange, pink, and purple in the clouds. Fireflies and flower petals drift through the air, adding whimsy and hope to the atmosphere of newfound freedom and expression.
